WEBVTT

00:00:01.504 --> 00:00:03.897
When you walk around
the place where you live,

00:00:03.921 --> 00:00:05.350
most of the times,

00:00:05.374 --> 00:00:07.539
you feel pretty safe
and comfortable, right?

00:00:08.839 --> 00:00:11.912
Now imagine if there were land mines

00:00:11.936 --> 00:00:14.109
buried right here,

00:00:14.133 --> 00:00:15.761
scattered around,

00:00:15.785 --> 00:00:18.269
and you'd never know
when you might step on one.

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:23.023
That's how it is for many
in my home country, Colombia.

00:00:23.393 --> 00:00:27.123
As a result of a 50-year
internal armed conflict,

00:00:27.147 --> 00:00:29.584
we have an undetermined
number of land mines

00:00:29.608 --> 00:00:31.505
buried throughout the countryside,